134
00:05:34,233 --> 00:05:37,102
JOY-ANN REID:<i> The BBC reports  all of the men in the  hermit kingdom</i>

135
00:05:37,201 --> 00:05:40,872
<i>must now sport the same haircut as the dear leader, Kim Jong-un.</i>

136
00:05:41,139 --> 00:05:43,742
